title: Ep103 Figure Skating Crimes
description: This week, the gals sharpen their skates and jump into some icy incidents. Crack open a bottle of Gorgeous Pinot Noir Chardonnay, practice your death spiral (check), and tune in for Figure Skating Crimes.
